Package it.polimi.ingsw.view.gui.scene

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    GenericSceneController
    Marker interface used to define all the scene controllers.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AlertSceneController
    This class implements the controller of a generic Alert Scene.
    BoardSceneController
    This class implements the controller of the scene of the board.
    ColorSceneController
    This class implements the controller of the scene where users pick their own color.
    ConnectSceneController
    This class implements the scene where users connect to the server.
    FirstPlayerSceneController
    This class implements the controller of the scene where the first player choose the first user.
    GodInfoSceneController
    This class implements the scene which shows information about a given god.
    GodsSceneController
    This class implements the scene where players choose their gods.
    LobbySceneController
    This class implements the scene where players wait for other players to join the game.
    LoginSceneController
    This class implements the scene where users choose their nicknames.
    MenuSceneController
    This class implements the main menu scene.
    PlayersNumberSceneController
    This class implements the scene where the game host chooses the number of players who are going to play.
    WinSceneController
    This class implements the scene which shows that a player has won the game.
